          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoq4h9RafCIDwkjPl3p_rqdk9o0sXB0J1RBjKrEgVUhJcPeSo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "What happened to Capsule?\n\nSeven years ago, Capsule was fantastic\u2014fast, reliable, and genuinely customer-focused.\n\nToday, it's the exact opposite.\n\nOver the last few years, I've repeatedly dealt with unavailable medications, last-minute cancellations, poor communication, and even security seal issues. At this point, reliability seems to be the exception rather than the rule.\n\nMy advice: don't just read the five-star reviews. Read the one-star reviews too. They tell a very different story and, in my experience, are much closer to the truth. Most of the glowing praise appears to be for the company Capsule USED TO BE\u2014not the company it has become.\n\nA pharmacy's job is simple: have the medication, communicate clearly, and deliver what was promised. Capsule struggles with all three.\n\nThere are enough headaches in life without adding your pharmacy to the list. Save yourself the frustration and look elsewhere.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkbVNURkxlRWxrTURoa1NuVkxkamxhUmkxM1gyYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa09d469a1f9ce774!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjdmSTFLeElkMDhkSnVLdjlaRi13X2c%7C%7C?hl=en",
