          "description": "My doctor suggested Capsule and I have been using them for years... I can't believe I ever stood on endless lines at Duane Reade or CVS before! Their delivery is quick and ontime, their customer service is amazing -- available by text, phone or email-- and a HUMAN responds quickly. They take my insurance as well as honoring GoodRX coupons. It's a great service and highly recommend!!!",
