          "description": "I spoke with a customer service rep from Capsule named Heaven, and she did an amazing/fantastic job. She walked me through the current status of my medications, as there is a nationwide shortage of some medications, which is not Capsule's fault, but due to that Heaven, the representative did a great job walking me through what\u2019s going on and how I can best position myself given the current climate for medication supplies for the wholesale supplier. I was very pleased with her help, as well as all the people who work at Capsule. Thanks, Heaven!",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWa1lUbEVZMjlOZW5KelMwdEZkbTl1ZG5NMlMwRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0xa09d469a1f9ce774!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjVkYTlEY29NenJzS0tFdm9udnM2S0E%7C%7C?hl=en",
