        {
          "username": "CEO CAPITALIST",
          "rating": 5,
          "contributor_id": "106837570115513955354",
          "user_review_count": 2,
          "user_photo_count": 0,
          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqMMNmLjpC3-kiHDL9kyuE4WCYq6jae8CUfQN7GFq5iTsqFdeo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100",
          "description": "I had the absolute pleasure of speaking with Joy at Capsule Pharmacy today, and she went above and beyond to help me with my medication pricing concerns. From the very first moment, Joy was incredibly courteous, patient, and professional. She listened carefully to my situation, quickly understood the issue, and took immediate action to resolve it.\nWhat truly stood out was how much she over-extended herself to make sure I was completely taken care of. She was efficient, thorough, and incredibly quick without ever making me feel rushed. Joy didn\u2019t just solve the problem\u2014she explained everything clearly, offered helpful options, and followed through until everything was sorted perfectly.\nThanks to Joy, I feel genuinely cared for as a customer. Her kindness, expertise, and dedication made a potentially stressful situation feel easy and reassuring. I can\u2019t recommend her highly enough!\nIf you\u2019re looking for exceptional service at Capsule Pharmacy, ask for Joy\u2014you\u2019ll be in the best hands possible. Thank you, Joy, for your outstanding help today! \u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50\u2b50",
